      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3, an analog masterpiece featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a Getrag six-speed manual transmission, delivering power to the pavement via a factory limited-slip differential. The engine's internals have been proactively addressed, including rod bearing replacement, ensuring the 8,000 RPM redline is met with absolute confidence. Maintained to concours standards with a factory-spec cooling system and perfectly balanced suspension geometry, this vehicle offers a pure, visceral driving experience that remains unparalleled in the modern era.",
